{"tid":572623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【寶島】台灣出現衛生紙搶購潮 當局稱下月中前不加價","createTime":"2018-02-25T17:20:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-25T21:12:41.000Z","uid":36551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d2fa8dd6bda125ffca47272fda6abf5f3bd234c8","tid":572623,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T17:20:25.000Z","msg":"台灣出現衛生紙搶購潮 當局稱下月中前不加價<br />\n25.02.2018 19:32<br />\n<br />\n國際紙漿價格持續上漲，台灣社會傳言廁紙及紙巾售價即將加價最多三成，引發民眾搶購，在多間大型超級市場，廁紙及紙巾被搶購一空；行政院消費者保護處傍晚表示，向四大賣場了解，到下月中前衛生紙價格不會變動，呼籲消費者無需恐慌搶購。發言人說，賣場承諾不會藉機囤積衛生紙，這幾天因為消費者搶購而缺貨，過幾天補貨後就會有貨售賣，當局亦會密切注意今次紙漿上漲會否帶動其他紙製品漲價。<br />\n<br />\n有立委批評消費者保護處，變相承認下月中後衛生紙要漲價，可能導致搶購潮更加瘋狂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=994508&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D994508%26csid%3D261_341&d=5us2%2BKFTpO%2FTuFLRTkIMH6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=fde3dc0c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=994508&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<br />\n手持10卷皇冠3層純白廁紙可以食幾多台妹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e229fd63d817b66f1dce48be5dafad2151df4e6","tid":572623,"uid":22566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T17:21:41.000Z","msg":"俾阿媽問你用咁多做咩就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98bbf69b1b1936257b106eca1a4ef7f248854207","tid":572623,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T17:22:31.000Z","msg":"國際紙漿價格持續上漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9309031c4c625c484897ff7d2b8e0b5e3ea1912f","tid":572623,"uid":36481,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T17:23:28.000Z","msg":"國際漿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes10.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc8c60a0c5938236d33a51dbcc8772d5e2793b6c","tid":572623,"uid":21035,"like":0,"dislike"